OL,5, The mother of Martha Mills, whose      
OL,6, preventable death in hospital has led  
OL,7, to calls for extra patients' rights,   
OL,8, has said she is to meet the health     
OL,9, secretary to discuss "Martha's Rule".  
OL,11,FIf introduced, it would give families a
OL,12,Fstatutory right to get a second opinion
OL,13,Fif they have concerns about care.      
OL,15,FMerope Mills said patients needed more 
OL,16,Fclarity and to feel empowered.         
OL,18,FHer daughter, Martha, died two years   
OL,19,Fago after failures in treating her     
OL,20,Fsepsis at King's College Hospital.     
